|------|--------|----------------|
| **Race conditions** | Duplicate charges if parallel calls succeed | Add idempotency keys |
| **Decimal precision** | Financial drift with floating point math | Use `BigDecimal` or cent-based integers |
| **Amount caps** | Fraud if unlimited charge amounts | Enforce per-transaction and daily limits |
| **Async retry** | Double-processing if caller retries on timeout | Implement exponential backoff with deduplication |
| **Customer state validation** | Charge on banned/frozen accounts | Add business rule validation layer |

